data.title: Wyatt Cahill - 2012 - Football
data.meta_description: Wyatt Cahill (97) DL  - Hoof Prints: Transfered to UB in 2011...willchallenge for a starting role in 2012... chose Buffalo for theopportunity to win a MAC Championship
data.text:
Hoof Prints: Transfered to UB in 2011...willchallenge for a starting role in 2012... chose Buffalo for theopportunity to win a MAC Championship and because of the Businessschool...major is business administration.

Junior (2011): Appeared in every game as areserve defensive lineman... made 14 total tackles (seven solo)...recovered a fumble in the season opener against Pittsburgh (9/3)...had three tackles and a pass breakup in a win over Stony Brook(9/10).

Previous School: Transfer from ScottsdaleCommunity College where he recorded 30 tackles, nine for losses,and four sacks in eight games

High School: Originally committed to Army outof high school where he was twice an All-Regional selection atCorona del Sol for coach Gary Venturo... earned three letters andwas captain for two seasons...also competed in the triple jump onthe track and field team for the Aztecs.
